  "all::Jan2020_P1H__Q12__p14-15__m05__Cumulative-Frequency-Diagrams": {
    "status": "checked",
    "source": "**Topic check:** Cumulative Frequency Diagrams. The tag is correct.\n\n**Solution**\n\nThere are \\(80\\) people.\n\nFor the interquartile range:\n\n\\[\nQ_1 \\text{ is at cumulative frequency }20\n\\]\n\n\\[\nQ_3 \\text{ is at cumulative frequency }60\n\\]\n\nFrom the graph,\n\n\\[\nQ_1\\approx 38,\\qquad Q_3\\approx 56\n\\]\n\n\\[\n\\text{IQR}\\approx 56-38=18\n\\]\n\nAt \\(50\\) minutes, the cumulative frequency is about \\(42\\).\n\nNo women took \\(50\\) minutes or less, so these \\(42\\) people are men.\n\n\\[\n0.6 \\times \\text{number of men}=42\n\\]\n\n\\[\n\\text{number of men}=\\frac{42}{0.6}=70\n\\]\n\n**Answers:** IQR about \\(18\\) minutes, and about \\(70\\) men.",
    "updated": "2026-05-06T18:13:48",
    "checked_by": "Dr Eslam Ahmed + Codex"
  },
