    "source": "**Topic check:** Statistics Toolkit. The tag is correct.\n\n**Solution**\n\nPut the marks in order:\n\n\\[\n5,\\ 7,\\ 11,\\ 12,\\ 13,\\ 14,\\ 15,\\ 16,\\ 17,\\ 18,\\ 18\n\\]\n\n\\[\nQ_1=11,\\qquad Q_3=17\n\\]\n\n\\[\n\\text{IQR}=17-11=6\n\\]\n\n**Answer:** \\(6\\).",
