    "source": "**Topic check:** Probability Diagrams - Venn & Tree Diagrams. The tag is correct.\n\n**Solution**\n\nThe missing branch probabilities are\n\n\\[\n0.1,\\quad 0.6\n\\]\n\nNovak wins both games with probability\n\n\\[\n0.7\\times 0.9=0.63\n\\]\n\n**Answer:** \\(0.63\\).",
